Module com.example.demo
Package com.example.demo.levels

Class LevelTwo

java.lang.Object
java.util.Observable
com.example.demo.levels.LevelParent
com.example.demo.levels.LevelTwo
public class LevelTwo extends LevelParent
The LevelTwo class represents the second level of the game, featuring enemy planes that the player must defeat to progress to the next level. The level ends when the player reaches the required kill count or loses all health.
